title: Crumbs Organic Bakehouse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Australian
description: Organic vegan bakery. Offers vegan sourdough bread, donuts, cakes, biscuits, pizza slices, and croissant. Take-away coffee using Syndicate blend or a weekly rotating single origin. Bonsoy and cow milk available (the only not vegan thing in the store). Second location in Union St, Ascot Vale.
